title: Z League

creator: Z League
descriptionHtml:
Z League adds a layer of casual competition to your favorite games. Whether you’re looking to meet other cool players to team up with, or just a simple way to track your game progress over time as you improve, we got you.

Currently supporting: Apex Legends, Call of Duty Warzone, Fortnite, Halo Infinite, and League of Legends.



THE FIRST EVER ALL-IN-ONE GAMING PROFILE

Simply and securely link your game profiles to your Z League profile to see all of your game stats, all in one place.

Add some details about yourself to let other gamers know how you play, what you like, what you don’t, and where you live to meet new friends and like-minded gamers.

Follow your friends and favorite creators to see their gaming activity and content, and build a following of your own!


TEAM UP WITH PLAYERS LIKE YOU

Playing with randoms just got a whole lot less random. Browse player profiles, invite people to Team Up, and chat with each other to coordinate before, during, and after your events.

Even if you’re not playing in one of our tournaments, Team Up is an awesome way to meet other cool players that you’ll want to play with again and again.


SKILL-BASED TOURNAMENTS FOR EVERYONE

Tournaments are broken down into skill-based divisions, so you’ll only play against other players and teams with a similar skill level to you. Bring your squad and play for keeps.

With more than a dozen tournament formats, at all times of the day, there’s always a way for you to drop in for some friendly, casual competition.


LIVE SCORING

The live scoreboard keeps tabs on all of the players or teams in your division, so you know your standings, and what you need to do to get ahead — and stay ahead.

Streaming? We got you. Add your stream right to the scoreboard to share out with all of your followers to see you in action.


ARCADE MODE

Don’t feel like getting sweaty? No sweat. Just play Arcade Mode to compete against yourself in a 60-minute kill race!


KEEP UP WITH ALL OF YOUR FOLLOWERS

Follow all of your friends and creators on Z League to see their recent activity, achievements, and streams.

Your feed brings all of your followers’ activity into one place so you can see what they’re playing and how they’re performing.

creator: Z League
descriptionHtml:
Join the ultimate gaming community with Z League - the app that brings gamers together like never before! Compete in thrilling tournaments, connect with like-minded players through LFG (looking for group), and share epic gaming clips with ease. Stay in the loop with live streams, chat with fellow gamers, and track your progress over time. With the convenient PLAY NOW feature, jump right into action whenever you're ready. Z League is THE super app for gamers of all levels. Level up your gaming experience and be part of the gaming revolution - DOWNLOAD NOW!

SKILL-BASED TOURNAMENTS FOR EVERYONE
Tournaments for : Warzone, Apex Legends, Halo Infinite, League of Legends (LoL), Valorant, PUBG, Destiny 2, and more!
Tournaments are segmented into SKILL-BASED divisions, so you’ll ONLY play against other players and teams with a similar skill level to you.

Play anytime, anywhere with our PLAY NOW feature, and earn Z Coins for each victory. Accumulate Z Coins and redeem them for thrilling rewards like scuff controllers, gaming PCs, Oculus devices, and gift cards.

LIVE SCORING
Stay on top of your game with LIVE SCORING and tracking by linking your game profiles securely to your Z League account

STREAMING
Are you a streamer? Showcase your skills to your followers by adding your stream directly to the scoreboard.

LFG! TEAM UP WITH PLAYERS LIKE YOU VIA LOOKING FOR GROUP (LFG)
Playing with randoms just got a whole lot less random! With our LFG feature, you can now browse player profiles using various filters such as gender, location, age, mic preference, and more. You can then easily connect with them by swiping right and invite them to join your tournaments! You can chat with your matches and new teammates directly in the Z League App.

THE FIRST-EVER ALL-IN-ONE GAMING PROFILE AND FEED
Customize your gaming profile with playstyle, preferences, location, unique avatars, and banners. Stay updated on your gaming community by following friends and favorite creators.

Unlike other social media platforms, our FEED is entirely gaming-related, free from all the unnecessary stuff. Share your best gaming moments, achievements, tips, and more on the FEED, connecting with gamers who truly understand your passion.

descriptionHtml:
Welcome to Z League – your go-to destination for social gaming and connecting with friends! Chat, play, and compete in a variety of thrilling games with your existing friends or meet new ones. Join millions of users around the world to have fun and forge lasting connections.

👥Build your Squad
Gather your friends on the Z League app. Personalize your avatar and unleash your creativity. Stay connected with in-app messaging and voice chat, creating a seamless and immersive gaming experience. With our multi-squad feature, you can build a squad for every facet of your life – from classmates to work friends to family. Connect and bring the fun to all the important relationships in your life.

🎮 Find fun for everyone
Experience endless entertainment with simple yet crazy-fun Z League games: Air Hockey, Bumbling Bee, Galaxy Glide, Solitaire, Swish, and WordHunt. No ads, no pay-to-win gimmicks – just pure fun for everyone. We're constantly adding new games to keep the excitement alive.

💪Compete for #1 on the Leaderboard
Let the scores speak for themselves! Engage in the Daily Rumble, where your squad competes in a randomly selected Z League game. A winner is crowned each day, securing the ultimate bragging rights.

🌍 Make New Gaming Friends
Find your gaming BFF with Z League's Looking for Group (LFG) feature. Specify preferences for games, region, and skill level to connect with new friends and enhance your gaming experience.

🏆 Join Skill-Based Tournaments
Compete in instant, skill-based tournaments for popular games like Apex Legends, Brawl Stars, Chess, Clash Royale, Destiny 2, Halo, League of Legends, PUBG, Teamfight Tactics, and Valorant, anytime. Play only against players at your level, so everyone has a chance to claim victory. No cheaters allowed with our proprietary anti-cheat detection mechanism.

Experience the magic of social gaming. It's time to play, connect, and compete together. Download Z League for FREE now and let the good times roll. 🚀
